The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Basu pact

 Calcutta, April 13: Jyoti Basu, as a Citu leader, today signed a tripartite agreement on behalf of 500 workers of a company for a salary hike and other benefits. The pact came in the wake of a protest by the workers without hampering production.

 Basu is the president of the Esab (I) Ltd Workers Union since 1948.




